  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the iron teppan skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the olive oil and swirl it around to coat the skillet.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the prosciutto slices and cook for 2 minutes on each side until crispy.",
    "Add the kombu sheets and cook for 1 minute on each side until fragrant.",
    "Add the cooked jasmine rice and stir to combine with the prosciutto and kombu.",
    "Add the crumbly feta cheese and stir to combine.",
    "Add the dried rose petals and stir to combine.",
    "Squeeze the freshly squeezed lemon juice over the top and stir to combine.",
    "Season with kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
